This script enhances Issue browsing for Jira.
And allows you to color Issues by status.

Note:
Current version of userscript works with Jira v5.2+.
For Jira v4.3 - 5.1 use userscript v1.4


Tested in:
- FireFox with Greacemonkey
- IE with Trixie
- Chrome as native extension


Note:
To allow this script work with Dashboard Widgets you should add column "Status" in the widget settings.


--------------------------
-- Possible Customization
--------------------------
Main configuration is placed in method initStatusColors().

1) You can add your custom statuses to coloring by enhancing object statusColorSettings.statusColors.
2) You can enable coloring by assignee by changing setting statusColorSettings.statusColors.colorByAssignee = true.
3) You can add your custom assignee to coloring by enhancing object statusColorSettings.assigneeColors.